response.overview: May 23rd, 2009 :: A wild relevos atomicos sees The Colony and The Super Smash Bros. team-up to take on The Osirian Portal and Los Ice Creams. F.I.S.T. fights The Future Is Now (Helios, Lince Dorado) and their mentor, Jigsaw! Delirious wrestles for the first time since falling under the spell of the Eye of Tyr. In the main event, Claudio Castagnoli wrestles Vin Gerard! Matches featured:  1. 2.0 vs Incoherence  2. Grizzly Redwood vs Hydra  3. Eddie Kingston vs Create-A-Wrestler  4. F.I.S.T. vs The Future Is Now  5. Arik Cannon vs Delirious  6. STIGMA vs Tim Donst  7. Los Ice Creams & The Osirian Portal vs The Colony & Super Smash Brothers  8. Vin Gerard vs Claudio Castagnoli.
response.title: Chikara Aniversario Yin
